sentences: Hanna Oleksiïvna Havrylets' (Ukrainian: Ганна Олексіївна Гаврилець; born 11 April 1958) is a Ukrainian composer.
She was awarded the Ukrainian Shevchenko National Prize in 1999 and became a Merited Artist of Ukraine in 2005.
